  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7, then cut your<strong> potatoes</strong> (skins on) into fries and peel and grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>fries</strong> to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong>, <strong>half </strong>the <strong>grated garlic</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for an initial 20-25 min or until golden – these are your <strong>garlic fries</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1708533092244-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1708533092244-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1708533092244-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1708533092244-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1708533092244-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>pork &</strong> <strong>beef mince </strong>(remove the paper if required) to a bowl with your <strong>dried oregano</strong>,<strong> remaining chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>beef</strong> <strong>stock mix </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Add a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up until thoroughly combined (clean hands are the best way!)</p><p>Divide and shape into 1 equal-sized patty per person and add to a separate <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (reserve the bowl)</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1708533100374-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1708533100374-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
