      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> tomato paste </strong>to the reserved bowl with your <strong>remaining beef stock mix</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>warm water</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>tomato sauce</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong> and pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
