      "instruction": "<p>Once the burger[s] is cooked, discard the excess juices on the tray</p><p>Top each patty with the<strong> tomato sauce</strong>, then the <strong>cheesy sauce</strong></p><p>Return the tray to the oven for a final 4-5 min or until everything is bubbling – this is your <strong>lasagne-style pork & beef burger</strong> <strong>patty</strong></p>",
