      "instruction": "<p>Once the fries are golden, remove from the oven and move to one side of the tray[s]</p><p>Add the<strong> brioche halves</strong> to the other side of the tray[s], cut-side up</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for a final 5 min or until warmed through</p>",
