    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build your burger, top the <strong>warmed brioche base</strong> with a <strong>lasagne-style pork & beef burger</strong> <strong>patty</strong> (and any extra sauce from the baking tray[s]!), then top with a <strong>warmed brioche lid </strong>– this is your <strong>Lasagne-style pork & beef burger</strong></p><p>Serve with the <strong>garlic fries </strong>and <strong>salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> to the salad and season with a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
